captions.text: Can you tell me anything about yourself?
Who you are?
How you got here?

I don't know how I get anywhere... without
my GPS.
Day one green. "Let's get started."
What's out there?
The Waze. Every morning when those doors open,

the Runners are instructed by a real-time
navigation system that supposedly gets them
to their destination quicker.
What happens to them?
In 75 feet turn right. What corridor, what corridor? Turn right at Beedle Blade Alley.
I just passed Beetle Blade Alley. Can't you tell me the shuckin' name before
I literally go right past it?
Who put us here? We don't know. All I can say is they had me turning down corridors
I never freakin' heard of.
It's a girl.
Thomas… Guide.
Never heard of it.
How is it different than Apple Maps? Maybe it's because
we're outsmarting the maze… together.
Bad timing Waze. Doesn't this kind of remind you of The Hunger Games?
Don't question the Waze Thomas. Look at that guy.
What happened to him? Mapquest.
Okay, I figured it out. All you need to do is- IN TEN FEET CONTINUE STRAIGHT.
Say that again. I said - IN FIVE FEET CONTINUE STRAIGHT.
One more time. Just find the - RECALCULATING ROUTE.
Now it won't start unless we stop running. Hit passenger, hit passenger!

If you're so smart can you give me a
landmark like a Quiznos or something?
Griever stopped on shoulder ahead.
Yeah right, I'm not falling for that one again…. Minho?
If you're gonna stay here I need to know that you're going to follow the directions.
Don't get all fussy halfway through and try to get on the freeway.
"You are nearing your destination."
I said stop navigation!
